{"word":"ἁρπαλίζω","slug":"ἁρπαλίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁρπαλίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρπάζω'><el>ἁρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to catch up, be eager to receive</i>, <el>τινὰ κωκυτοῖς</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to exact greedily</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}